WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.000
Look at your feet. Every day — it's the habit that saves toes.

00:07.000 --> 00:13.000
Small things matter, because small things can become big things fast.

00:13.000 --> 00:21.000
Check the top, the bottom, the toes, and the heels.

00:21.000 --> 00:31.000
Look for cuts, redness, swelling, blisters, cracks, sore spots, or color changes.

00:31.000 --> 00:39.000
With neuropathy, you may not feel an injury — so the daily look is what catches it.

00:39.000 --> 00:50.000
Warm water. Dry well, between the toes. Clean socks. Good shoes. And never barefoot.

00:50.000 --> 00:58.000
Diabetes is a 24/7 job. You don't have to carry it alone.

00:58.000 --> 01:05.000
LocalDiabetic. We just help you carry the day. Win big.
